Contains:   

   The contents of the first Fantagraphics Omnibus volume, which collects the
   original graphic novel, the first fourteen issues of the ongoing series,
   independently published between 1997 and 2002, and two short stories. Here,
   the omnibus has been disassembled again, per narrative continuity, and the
   black-and-white artwork was recompressed into the modern .webp format.

   Size reduction: ~70% | Quality reduction: 2/10 (differences are slight and rare)
